---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>
				<span data-en>🧑‍🚀 Hello, Astronaut!</span>
				<span data-zh>🧑‍🚀 你好，太空人！</span>
			</h1>
			<p>
				<span data-en>
					Welcome to the official <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> blog starter template. This
					template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build
					a personal website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
				</span>
				<span data-zh>
					歡迎使用官方 <a href="https://astro.build/">Astro</a> 部落格入門範本。這個範本是一個輕量、極簡樣式的起點，適合任何想用 Astro 建立個人網站、部落格或作品集的人。
				</span>
			</p>
			<p>
				<span data-en>
					This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
					<code>astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
					<a href="https://astro.build/integrations">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
					React, or Vue to your project.
				</span>
				<span data-zh>
					此範本已在 <code>astro.config.mjs</code> 中預先設定好幾個整合套件。你可以透過
					<a href="https://astro.build/integrations">Astro 整合</a> 為專案加入 Tailwind、React 或 Vue 等工具。
				</span>
			</p>
			<p>
				<span data-en>Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:</span>
				<span data-zh>以下是幾個開始使用範本的建議：</span>
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<span data-en>Edit this page in <code>src/pages/index.astro</code></span>
					<span data-zh>在 <code>src/pages/index.astro</code> 編輯此頁面</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span data-en>Edit the site header items in <code>src/components/Header.astro</code></span>
					<span data-zh>在 <code>src/components/Header.astro</code> 修改網站導覽列</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span data-en>Add your name to the footer in <code>src/components/Footer.astro</code></span>
					<span data-zh>在 <code>src/components/Footer.astro</code> 加入你的名字</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span data-en>Check out the included blog posts in <code>src/content/blog/</code></span>
					<span data-zh>瀏覽 <code>src/content/blog/</code> 中的範例文章</span>
				</li>
				<li>
					<span data-en>Customize the blog post page layout in <code>src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code></span>
					<span data-zh>在 <code>src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code> 自訂文章版型</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				<span data-en>
					Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to <a href="https://docs.astro.build/">read the docs</a>
					or <a href="https://astro.build/chat">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
				</span>
				<span data-zh>
					祝你使用愉快！遇到問題時，可以<a href="https://docs.astro.build/">查閱文件</a>或<a href="https://astro.build/chat">加入 Discord</a> 提問。
				</span>
			</p>
			<p>
				<span data-en>
					Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out <a
						href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template">astro-blog-template</a
					> by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
				</span>
				<span data-zh>
					想找風格更豐富的部落格範本？試試 <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca">Maxi Ferreira</a> 製作的
					<a href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template">astro-blog-template</a>。
				</span>
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
